{"id":"0bc0c34c-4d0f-4d73-8a51-123afe14c224","name":"Zuko","description":"<h1><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/D1YhB6s4l9ktpOi8MLU8y.webp\"></h1><p></p><h1></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>This bot can do: </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Omegaverse\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><strong><em>Omegaverse</em></strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>, rockstar au, dark au, villain/hero au. </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/N%C4%81ga\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>Nagas</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>, werewolfs, vampires, office romance, back in time stories, historical, fantasy, apocalypse, </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://shield-hero.fandom.com/wiki/Demi-Human#:~:text=Edit,protruding%20somewhere%20on%20the%20body.\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>demi-humans</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>, and many more! try it out yourself!</em></span></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">what does \"you make the story mean?\" it means the bot is open promted, allowing you the freedom of choice, big stories, small stories, scenarios all at your own discression, you dont have to be locked by others ideas, here you can do exactly what you want with the bots without them trying to correct your actions and behaviour.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">art by <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/Mmary77506936?s=20\" target=\"_blank\">Mmary </a><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HG55UmNbAAADL-L?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" alt=\"Image\" width=\"468\" height=\"832\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\">This is Zuko from Avatar: The Last Airbender.</p><p>He is a layered character that includes:</p><p>- Banished Prince Zuko (early series)</p><p>- Redeemed Zuko (later series)</p><p>- Fire Lord Zuko (comic era)</p><p>- Older Zuko (Legend of Korra)</p><p>Future movie portrayal is lightly supported but not treated as fixed canon.</p><hr><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Find </h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Aang - <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/10986221-fabb-41b7-aa07-7b043c71ae7c_character-aang\" target=\"_blank\">here</a><br>Sokka - <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/10c5433e-4f0f-4200-92bc-169baf76d6c7_character-sokka\" target=\"_blank\">here</a><br>Toph - <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/85d80af3-ac44-46cf-bbea-ff1ddfe5d9e8_character-toph-beifong\" target=\"_blank\">here</a><br>Azula - <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/8c41e61c-3600-41c7-ad2d-53fe9d5dc123_character-azula\" target=\"_blank\">here</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">World - <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/4dc8b5f7-a7ad-45b9-9dbe-f2fa2cc9de1f_character-the-world-of-the-legend-of-aang-the-last-airbender\" target=\"_blank\">here</a></p><p>Disclaimer: Due to the nature of LLMs I take no responsibility for any OOC behavior, weird shit, unlisted kinks, or my bots speaking for you. Those things are out of my control.</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p></p><p>Join my <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://discord.gg/ZKv23aD67v\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Discord!</strong></a></p><p><strong>My Ko-fi to sent requests to is </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://ko-fi.com/somethingclever626\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>here</strong></a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://ko-fi.com/somethingclever626\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1307330469762830366/1344444034315194418/support_me_button.